Name Rascal/Libraries/Benchmark
Synopsis Functions for time measurement and benchmarking.
Syntax import Benchmark;
Details benchmark cpuTime realTime systemTime userTime
Description Provides the following functions:
  • benchmark: Measure and report the execution time of name:void-closure pairs
  • cpuTime: Measuring CPU time.
  • realTime: Current time in milliseconds.
  • systemTime: Measuring system time.
  • userTime: Measuring user time.
